latestIgtvVideos.title: Empyreal ShowBuzz
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The Pink City witnessed a class-apart and a one-of-a-kind gathering, organized by Empyreal Club at the landmark Raj Mandir on 18th Sep 2021. 

Empyreal Showbuzz was a housefull edition with unlimited laughter and ecstatic entertainment. 

Where the popular stand-up comedy acts Manish Tyagi and Parvinder Singh brought a bundle of laughter to the people, the Live Band performance by All India Permit was a truly entrancing one making everyone jive. 

Through Empyreal ShowBuzz, the Club will introduce a mix of engagements such as Talk Shows, Fashion, Food & Lifestyle events, bringing a high-street uber culture in Jaipur.

latestPosts.caption:
A dream turned into reality...✨🎬

After over three months of planning, prep, and pouring our hearts into every detail, this day felt like pure magic. To finally see it all come alive and to do so alongside the phenomenal @ayushmannk, was beyond special. 🙌

Working with him on something truly exceptional… something that blends emotion, energy, and purpose, will stay with me forever. From the first shot to the final frame, it was a surreal experience to witness his infectious onset vibe, unmatched professionalism, and deeply grounded humility. 🌟

What moved me even more was watching every single person, from DOPs to spot boys work with the same fire and focus. A masterclass in what it really takes to bring a vision to life. 🎥🔥

Grateful for the journey, the conversations, the learning, and those fleeting but unforgettable moments with one of the finest in the business. The big reveal is on its way… and I can’t wait to share it with you all 🚀

Love on the go. Magic in the making.✨ Celebrate Life Every Moment | EmpyrealClub
